//for Swagger
https://www.npmjs.com/package/swagger-jsdoc :- 
1. npm module document are code
2. Generates swagger documentation from the comments in our code 
(this is what gives autogenartion of our documentation its power )
npm install --save-dev swagger-jsdoc


https://www.npmjs.com/package/swagger-ui-express
1. help us document are code and genrates swagger documentation from the comments
in our code 
npm install --save-dev swagger-ui-express
